<span class='line-number'>12</span>
<span class='line-number'>13</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='bash'><span class='line'>&lt;/p&gt;
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'>&lt;p&gt;apt-get install kernel-package libncurses5-dev fakeroot wget bzip2
</span><span class='line'>cp linux-3.x.x /usr/src
</span><span class='line'><span class="nb">cd</span> /usr/src/linux-3.x.x
</span><span class='line'>make menuconfig
</span><span class='line'>make modules
</span><span class='line'>make modules_install
</span><span class='line'>make
</span><span class='line'>make install
</span><span class='line'>sudo mkinitramfs -o /boot/initrd.img-3.x.x
</span><span class='line'>sudo update-initramfs -c -k 3.x.x
</span><span class='line'>sudo update-grub2
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></notextile></div></p>

<hr />

<p> <!--more--></p>

<p>卸载：</p>

<p> custom compiled kernel you need to remove following files/dirs:</p>

<ul>
<li>/boot/vmlinuz*KERNEL-VERSION*</li>
<li>/boot/initrd*KERNEL-VERSION*</li>
<li>/boot/System-map*KERNEL-VERSION*</li>
<li>/boot/config-*KERNEL-VERSION*</li>
<li>/lib/modules/*KERNEL-VERSION*/</li>
<li>Update grub configuration file /etc/grub.conf or /boot/grub/menu.lst
to point to correct kernel version.</li>
</ul>

